body: "Re-audit Decision Record:\n\nSYSTEM HEALTH: All systems operational. No regressions found.\n\nVERIFICATION GATES PASSED:\n- Build + Typecheck: clean\n- Test suite: 84 files, 1177 tests, all pass\n- Security scan: zero findings\n- Version policy: 2026.5.2 valid\n- NPX smoke: pass\n- Package: 415 files\n\nFUNCTIONAL AREAS VERIFIED:\n- CLI lifecycle: init/create/claim/update/comments/notes/learnings/files/close/release\n- Output modes: TOON (default), JSON, quiet, help, contracts\n- SDK: 70+ typed exports, 9 capability types, defineExtension helper\n- Search: keyword 2.3s, semantic 2.1s, hybrid 2.0s (Ollama Qwen + LanceDB)\n- Reindex: 668 items, keyword 1.6s, semantic 35s\n- Calendar: agenda/week/month views, recurrence, filters, markdown format\n- Telemetry: enabled by default, opt-out, scrubbing, retry, queue flush\n- Sentry: PmCliError filtering, data scrubbing, DSN configured\n- CI/CD: timeout-minutes, multi-OS/Node matrix, SHA-pinned actions, provenance\n\nLIVE INFRASTRUCTURE:\n- 9 Docker containers running (healthy)\n- Telemetry API: 200 OK\n- Grafana v11.6.14: database OK\n- RabbitMQ: queue 0/0\n- Postgres: 34981 events, 1367 unique installations\n- Sentry: 0 unresolved issues, release tracked\n\nRESIDUAL RISKS:\n- command-aware.ts buildCommandAwareEnvelope is unused dead code (reserved for future)\n- Historical pm item comments contain legacy host paths (redaction notes appended, history JSONL immutable)\n\nNEXT ITERATION BACKLOG:\n- Integrate command-aware output module into live CLI commands\n- Consider search performance optimization for larger corpora"
